	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, there are probably a million different things that you could do at 34.&nbsp;&nbsp;For me, personally, Dawnshroud Peaks on Luclin was a goldmine.  Not much loot to be had, but the xp was good.  If I couldn't find a group, I would just root/nuke mushrooms or zelniaks.  <br>With two zones to run to if you get in trouble, non-aggroing mobs (well, watch out for the wolves and shrooms, but zelniaks won't aggro), and several safe pulling/medding spots, the xp just moves there whether in a group or solo.  Most of my time from 30 to 39 was spent there.<br><br>Hope that helps!<br><br>Kantrall Thurnkiel<br>41st Wizard<br>Clan of the Wulf<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
